  "detailed_description": "Entangle tasks you with maneuvering a number of line segments along their designated paths until they reach their goals.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhilst this might sound like a simple premise on the surface, it evolves into quite a challenge when it is combined with a variety of increasingly complex mechanics and clever level design.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOver the course of 50 levels, your experience of the game will transition from soothing to challenging to head-scratching.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIncludes a colour blind mode.",
